<div class='col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1'>
  <h4>{{t "A Little About Core" key="a_little_about_core"}}</h4>
</div>
<div class='col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1'>
  <img src={{path "walkthrough/core_words.gif"}} style='width: 100%;' >
</div>
<div class='col-sm-5'>
  <div class="setup-core-callout">
    <span class="setup-core-callout__label" aria-hidden="true">{{t "Core words" key="core_words"}}</span>
    <p class="setup-core-callout__p">{{t "Core words are high-frequency, everyday words with multiple meanings. They help communicators participate across the whole day—not just in one or two situations." key="core_1"}}</p>
    <p class="setup-core-callout__p">{{t "Core words let people build their own sentences instead of relying on a long list of pre-made phrases." key="core_2"}}</p>
    <p class="setup-core-callout__p setup-core-callout__p--tip">{{t "Choose a vocabulary set with enough core words for the communicator to grow into—and plan with the end in mind." key="core_3"}}</p>
  </div>
</div>